Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:42.76,Midcard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(110,435)}3D Maneuver Gear Training (pt 2)\NStrong body and legwork, good spatial perception, \Nand mental strength to withstand panic are essential.
